title: The Last Adventurer
description: The Last Adventurer Manhwa The gate opened and the era of adventure began. An era when everything fell apart, a time of dread, desperation, and misery. And— An era when everyone gave up trying to fight back. But there was one adventurer who fought back till the very end. “You are the only one left, El Palm. You’re the last adventurer.” The moment the history of the adventurer came to an end, the Last Adventurer brought the whole story back to its starting point.
